N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 3 ยง 412.4 - Certification

State Regulations

The secretary of the fund shall certify to the
superintendent that the events referred to in section
412.3
of this Part have taken
place. Thereafter, upon the filing of the superintendent's approval thereof in
the office of the superintendent, the fund shall be
dissolved. Notes
